Name: RemoteCompanion
Depends: mobilesubstrate
Version: 3.4.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: A modern Activator replacement for rootless and rootful jailbreaks. iOS 17 compatible. Bind triggers like Power/Volume buttons, and Status Bar gestures to system actions, Siri automation, and custom TCP commands. Touch ID triggers removed for iOS 17 compatibility. https://github.com/saihgupr/RemoteCompanion
